{"tid":1357063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請唔好再講警黑勾結 係官警黑勾結！","createTime":"2019-07-23T15:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:04:51.000Z","uid":27617,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a73a533f5b9c3ea323a78c919b7ffb0ee71460ba","tid":1357063,"uid":27617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"唔係警黑勾結咁簡單<br />\n係官警黑！<br />\n呢件事明顯係何君堯、中聯辦同港府策劃既恐怖襲擊，你不斷叫警黑勾結只係將焦點放係黑警同黑社會<br />\n但咁樣唔係事實既全部<br />\n如果最後只有盧偉聰下台或元朗指揮官辭咁點？係咪就回應左訴求？<br />\n必須要講明係官警黑！呢個政府係由上而下咁腐朽，一定要拉埋政府落水，對準政權！"},{"pid":"f5ca745831ed6bd8e3e4d2407d6548f504fbbdfe","tid":1357063,"uid":27617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:53:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0258eb839b26cc197c2e1bfe8beab78d543b6f5d","tid":1357063,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查官警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9ee456232fc8fb44912db96232e687bfb542b69e","tid":1357063,"uid":27617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:54:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dea0c284ed594f2ec5bf195c0901c1f20ef17661","tid":1357063,"uid":27617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:54:29.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"c7528db44ccf3f9e8b8ad57933b82c7696c0707c","tid":1357063,"uid":264336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:54:39.000Z","m